205
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:54,590
Sergeant First Class Park Beom-gu,
Military Police.

206
00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:56,590
Wasn't this man under investigation?

207
00:13:56,670 --> 00:13:57,800
