in the mission.

209
00:14:00,510 --> 00:14:02,850
-They're going to provide assistance.
-Yes.

210
00:14:09,190 --> 00:14:11,110
Private Kim Ru-ri
has always been a soldier

211
00:14:11,190 --> 00:14:13,020
