-Go to hell.

240
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:56,750
-Yes, but there's an issue.
-What?

241
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:59,920
-Well, he can't… he can't speak.
-Oh, great, why not?

242
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:02,090
