245
00:16:06,180 --> 00:16:07,810
Sergeant Park, look.

246
00:16:07,890 --> 00:16:08,720
Hurry!

247
00:16:08,810 --> 00:16:11,100
-Get over here.
-Well, I have to call you back.

248
00:16:12,770 --> 00:16:13,890
-That's crazy,
-Uh-huh.

249
00:16:13,980 --> 00:16:16,560
-Hey!
-He's completely lost it.

250
00:16:16,650 --> 00:16:18,230
