251
00:16:19,230 --> 00:16:20,070
This is creepy.

252
00:16:20,150 --> 00:16:22,440
Hello, my name is Kim Ru-ri.

253
00:16:22,530 --> 00:16:24,450
ARMED DESERTER KIM RU-RI
INTERNET LIVE STREAM

254
00:16:24,530 --> 00:16:25,780
I'm the armed deserter.

255
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:31,370
I did shoot my senior officers that day.

256
00:16:33,710 --> 00:16:35,620
They harassed me, nonstop.

257
00:16:40,130 --> 00:16:42,880
