274
00:17:40,610 --> 00:17:41,440
Oh!

275
00:17:42,270 --> 00:17:43,320
Are you okay?

276
00:17:46,860 --> 00:17:49,160
I'll tell the truth of how it went down!

277
00:17:51,330 --> 00:17:53,620
You lying motherfuckers!

278
00:18:05,260 --> 00:18:06,510
