out of control.

282
00:18:18,520 --> 00:18:19,980
He's in over his head.

283
00:18:27,780 --> 00:18:29,070
-Come with me.
-Huh?

284
00:18:29,570 --> 00:18:30,660
What is it?

285
00:19:02,350 --> 00:19:03,520
Honestly…

286
00:19:07,690 --> 00:19:08,940
I'm so scared.

287
00:19:12,820 --> 00:19:14,910
When I think about…

288
00:19:19,410 --> 00:19:20,370
