289
00:19:26,210 --> 00:19:27,840
that my child could…

290
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:32,970
could actually do something so terrible.

291
00:19:48,860 --> 00:19:51,450
My Ru-ri was always gentle and kind.

292
00:19:51,950 --> 00:19:53,360
This is my fault.

293
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:59,410
What will happen to Ru-ri now, huh?

294
00:20:00,370 --> 00:20:01,540
What will they do?

295
00:20:04,250 --> 00:20:05,380
He can still live though?

296
00:20:13,260 --> 00:20:14,430
Save my son.

297
00:20:19,510 --> 00:20:20,600
Please.

298
00:20:22,230 --> 00:20:24,270
I'm begging you, please save him.

299
00:20:27,560 --> 00:20:30,650
HIGH PROSECUTOR'S OFFICE
MILITARY INVESTIGATOR'S ROOM

300
00:20:30,730 --> 00:20:32,320
