301
00:20:34,570 --> 00:20:38,080
MILITARY USE
AUXILIARY STORAGE UNIT

302
00:20:49,210 --> 00:20:51,800
Yeah? The materials
are ready to go, right?

303
00:20:52,670 --> 00:20:54,340
What are you talking about?

304
00:20:56,590 --> 00:20:57,760
I'm on my way.

305
00:20:58,390 --> 00:21:00,260
Those useless bastards, jeez.

306
00:21:04,020 --> 00:21:06,980
Why is he here all alone
with all that's going on right now?

307
00:21:07,060 --> 00:21:09,560
It's his office, he probably needed
to get his toothbrush.

308
00:21:09,650 --> 00:21:11,780
This isn't the barracks.
This is Armed Forces HQ.

309
00:21:11,860 --> 00:21:13,650
We could end up in deep shit.

310
00:21:13,740 --> 00:21:15,070
Are you coming or not?

311
00:21:16,740 --> 00:21:18,910
Oh, God.

312
00:21:23,830 --> 00:21:25,210
Go in already.

313
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:31,090
We've got these bastards.

314
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:33,920
