316
00:21:35,840 --> 00:21:36,800
CLASSIFIED DOCUMENT

317
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:39,760
Even a general could go down
for keeping a secret like this.

318
00:21:39,850 --> 00:21:41,140
Any guess on the password?

319
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:43,520
Come on, Sergeant Park,
