320
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:45,850
-I don't know.
-Why not type in Hwarang cigarettes.

321
00:21:45,930 --> 00:21:47,600
Jesus, help me out--

322
00:21:52,230 --> 00:21:53,780
What the hell are you doing?

323
00:22:03,620 --> 00:22:05,290
"What the hell are you doing?"

324
00:22:06,460 --> 00:22:08,710
