334
00:22:36,900 --> 00:22:38,820
Hey! What are you doing?

335
00:22:48,750 --> 00:22:49,920
You two idiots.

336
00:22:57,550 --> 00:22:59,880
You son of a bitch.

337
00:23:10,060 --> 00:23:12,520
It's time, get the soldiers in position.

338
00:23:16,190 --> 00:23:18,440
He hasn't been using the buses
or the subway.

339
00:23:18,990 --> 00:23:21,320
It seems he's more cautious
than we thought.

340
00:23:22,860 --> 00:23:24,530
