341
00:23:25,120 --> 00:23:27,330
Even with the help of the D.P. teams
from nearby units…

342
00:23:28,450 --> 00:23:29,580
…we need more time.

343
00:23:30,620 --> 00:23:34,840
I mean, if you keep moving so slow,
how do you expect to catch him?

344
00:23:35,710 --> 00:23:38,710
Kim Ru-ri's rifle was found.
He must have discarded it.

345
00:23:39,210 --> 00:23:40,470
So that's good news.

346
00:23:40,550 --> 00:23:42,800
Well, don't tell the press
about it.

347
00:23:43,390 --> 00:23:44,930
There's nothing to be gained.

348
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:48,310
As for now…

349
00:23:49,220 --> 00:23:52,350
the bait is already set. Is it a go?

350
00:24:02,700 --> 00:24:05,160
PRINCESS

351
00:24:10,500 --> 00:24:13,250
Hello, honey.
Sorry, I'm working right now.

352
00:24:13,330 --> 00:24:15,460
Mom, Dad needs your help.

353
00:24:16,420 --> 00:24:17,380
What's this about?

354
00:24:17,460 --> 00:24:19,750
I don't know. He just said
to open the door for him.

355
00:24:19,840 --> 00:24:21,720
I'm confused. How is he calling, huh?

356
00:24:42,690 --> 00:24:44,400
It's the same as it always was.

357
00:24:45,110 --> 00:24:47,280
You cause a mess,
and I have to clean it up.

358
00:24:48,910 --> 00:24:50,370
So how did you call Jin- a?

359
00:24:50,950 --> 00:24:52,700
I blocked your number on her phone.

360
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:59,670
You have two phones?
So you can still talk to the kids?

361
00:24:59,750 --> 00:25:01,960
Hey, I had some extra cash
so I bought a burner.

362
00:25:02,050 --> 00:25:03,050
Damn you…

363
00:25:03,630 --> 00:25:04,550
Sorry.

364
00:25:08,350 --> 00:25:11,930
Colonel Seo, let us help you
locate Kim Ru-ri.

365
00:25:12,020 --> 00:25:13,520
That won't be necessary.

366
00:25:16,350 --> 00:25:18,060
The deserter will come to us.

367
00:25:20,150 --> 00:25:21,440
You can't be serious.

368
00:25:23,690 --> 00:25:25,280
What have you done now?

369
00:25:29,740 --> 00:25:31,490
After the spring rain ends,

370
00:25:31,580 --> 00:25:34,000
I think it'll be nice to go
and watch the cherry blossoms…

371
00:25:34,080 --> 00:25:35,120
Welcome, sir.

372
00:25:35,210 --> 00:25:38,330
Cherry blossoms are expected to reach
peak bloom on April 4th…

373
00:25:38,420 --> 00:25:41,290
-Do you have, uh, inhaler?
-…on April 10th in the central regions…

374
00:25:41,380 --> 00:25:42,800
Let me check, one moment.

375
00:25:42,880 --> 00:25:44,050
…favorite time of the year.

376
00:25:44,130 --> 00:25:45,840
We can expect some rain before then,

377
00:25:45,920 --> 00:25:47,930
so don't forget your umbrella.

378
00:25:48,010 --> 00:25:48,840
This just in.

379
00:25:48,930 --> 00:25:51,890
We have an update on the shooting
in the 18th Armored Brigade.

380
00:25:51,970 --> 00:25:54,560
A violent scene erupted in front
of the home of Private Kim,

381
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:56,430
the deserter who murdered fellow soldiers.

382
00:25:56,520 --> 00:25:58,730
Here with the details
is Reporter Kim Mun-su.

383
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:02,150
This was
a peaceful neighborhood

384
00:26:02,230 --> 00:26:04,820
until this morning,
when a dangerous scene unfolded.

385
00:26:05,570 --> 00:26:08,200
Family members of the victims
of the recent shooting incident

386
00:26:08,280 --> 00:26:10,240
held a protest in front of the restaurant,

387
00:26:10,320 --> 00:26:12,580
shouting abusive chants
and throwing stones.

388
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:15,870
This footage was taken in front
of a restaurant this morning.

389
00:26:15,950 --> 00:26:17,620
A woman comes out of the restaurant,

390
00:26:17,710 --> 00:26:20,540
and one of the victims' family member
slaps her in the face.

391
00:26:21,040 --> 00:26:23,500
The unapologetic attitude
of Private Kim Ru-ri's mother

392
00:26:23,590 --> 00:26:26,380
outraged the victims' families…

393
00:26:26,460 --> 00:26:29,260
which eventually led
to a violent commotion.

394
00:26:30,470 --> 00:26:32,430
This footage spread quickly
on social media,

395
00:26:32,510 --> 00:26:33,760
and people are outraged.

396
00:26:33,850 --> 00:26:34,680
Mom…

397
00:26:35,180 --> 00:26:38,060
-Some think the actions against the woman…
-Those sons of bitches!

398
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:39,560
Those assholes!

399
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:41,150
Other's understand the backlash.

400
00:26:42,940 --> 00:26:44,940
-Mom.
-The footage has already aired.

401
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:48,400
They didn't blur her face in the video.

402
00:26:49,150 --> 00:26:50,490
He has to show up now.

403
00:26:51,530 --> 00:26:52,910
And we'll be ready for him.

404
00:26:53,700 --> 00:26:56,700
How could you do something like this
when you're a mother?

405
00:26:57,370 --> 00:26:58,830
You can't be serious?

406
00:26:58,910 --> 00:27:00,210
I explained to you,

407
00:27:00,290 --> 00:27:02,710
if someone dies
or gets hurt in this situation…

408
00:27:02,790 --> 00:27:05,460
We should make sure Kim Ru-ri
doesn't get hurt either.

409
00:27:06,840 --> 00:27:08,260
That's just as important.

410
00:27:12,470 --> 00:27:14,300
You call yourself soldiers.

411
00:27:16,010 --> 00:27:20,140
And yet here you are defending Kim Ru-ri,
who murdered fellow soldiers.

412
00:27:20,850 --> 00:27:23,860
He could throw a grenade
at innocent people any moment.

413
00:27:28,110 --> 00:27:29,690
Continue to wait in here.

414
00:27:31,450 --> 00:27:33,370
I met him before all this.

415
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:42,620
Kim Ru-ri and I have met.

416
00:27:46,340 --> 00:27:47,380
So are you Luffy?

417
00:27:52,630 --> 00:27:53,800
Yes, sir, I'm Luffy.

418
00:27:56,050 --> 00:27:59,020
We knew that there was an issue
at that base, but…

419
00:28:02,770 --> 00:28:04,520
we couldn't do anything about it.

420
00:28:09,900 --> 00:28:13,410
I'm asking for one more chance,
to see if we can persuade him.

421
00:28:15,780 --> 00:28:17,280
It's worth a try, ma'am.

422
00:28:25,420 --> 00:28:27,670
Please help us out here. Yeah?

423
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:35,760
Well, I'm sorry.

424
00:28:40,100 --> 00:28:41,060
Don't let them leave.

425
00:28:41,140 --> 00:28:42,350
-Yes, ma'am.
-Yes, ma'am.

426
00:28:58,780 --> 00:29:01,120
Our only play left
is with your cell phone.

427
00:29:02,580 --> 00:29:03,870
So what's your plan now?

428
00:29:05,250 --> 00:29:09,420
If Kim Ru-ri decides to show up
to an angry mob, they'll put him down.

429
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:13,970
We can't allow it.

430
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:26,140
Don't end up
with these fucking regrets like I did.

431
00:29:27,560 --> 00:29:28,400
Okay?

432
00:29:39,950 --> 00:29:42,790
If it was that hard on him,
he should have just deserted.

433
00:29:43,660 --> 00:29:45,330
Why shoot all those people?

434
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:51,000
And if he was going to do that,
he should have just died with them.

435
00:29:53,840 --> 00:29:54,880
Don't you think?

436
00:29:56,470 --> 00:29:57,300
Oh…

437
00:29:58,050 --> 00:29:58,930
Yes, sir.

438
00:30:07,190 --> 00:30:09,940
The general is approaching.
Check the positions of the soldiers.

439
00:30:10,900 --> 00:30:12,940
Our ETA is 30 minutes from now.

440
00:30:13,020 --> 00:30:15,030
-Attention!
-Attention!

441
00:30:15,110 --> 00:30:18,820
As of this very moment,
this operation area is tier one.

442
00:30:18,910 --> 00:30:21,120
Establish a one kilometer perimeter.

443
00:30:21,200 --> 00:30:23,660
No one other than
military personnel is allowed.

444
00:30:23,740 --> 00:30:25,580
-Understand?
-Yes, sir!

445
00:30:26,620 --> 00:30:27,660
Block them, block them!

446
00:30:27,750 --> 00:30:30,210
-Hey! Stop this!
-What are you doing? We have questions.

447
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:33,000
-Push! Push!
-Hey! Hurry up!

448
00:30:33,090 --> 00:30:34,550
Hey, what are you doing?

449
00:30:34,630 --> 00:30:36,010
What is all this?

450
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:38,260
-Stop! Get back!
-Secure the perimeter!

451
00:30:38,340 --> 00:30:39,970
-Yes, sir!
-Don't just stand there.

452
00:30:40,050 --> 00:30:41,340
Push them out, you idiot!

453
00:30:41,930 --> 00:30:43,390
What's the point of all this?

454
00:30:43,930 --> 00:30:45,220
-Hey!
-Mm… Mm…

455
00:30:45,310 --> 00:30:46,390
Sergeant Han?

456
00:30:47,560 --> 00:30:50,310
Hey, what are you doing?
Put this on and get ready!

457
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:59,200
Sniper Two, you're out.

458
00:31:07,250 --> 00:31:09,080
Everyone,
back to your positions!

459
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:10,290
Yes, sir!

460
00:31:10,370 --> 00:31:14,630
DO NOT ENTER

461
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:16,840
Sergeant Han.

462
00:31:17,760 --> 00:31:18,590
You okay, man?

463
00:31:19,800 --> 00:31:21,930
Hey. Hey, get the fuck up.

464
00:31:22,010 --> 00:31:25,010
I need assistance here.
He's not feeling well!

465
00:31:25,890 --> 00:31:28,060
Hey, shut up, asshole.
He'll sit out for now.

466
00:31:28,140 --> 00:31:30,810
Get over here,
you undisciplined shitheads!

467
00:31:32,900 --> 00:31:34,150
Fuck this.

468
00:31:37,610 --> 00:31:38,610
Rest up.

469
00:31:43,530 --> 00:31:45,370
Stay put. Come on, sir.

470
00:31:49,950 --> 00:31:52,540
You're obviously not well.
How could you help like this?

471
00:31:54,210 --> 00:31:55,840
All units…

472
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:57,840
stand by for the order to shoot.

473
00:31:58,460 --> 00:32:00,590
I repeat.

474
00:32:00,670 --> 00:32:02,760
-Stand by for the order to shoot.
-Come on.

475
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:04,180
Don't worry about it.

476
00:32:05,850 --> 00:32:07,180
It'll all be fine.

477
00:32:12,190 --> 00:32:14,440
We're three minutes out.
Get ready, soldiers!

478
00:32:14,520 --> 00:32:15,860
-Stand by!
-Yes, sir!

479
00:32:15,940 --> 00:32:18,360
-Where is she?
-We have to do a thorough search.

480
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:22,490
There's his mother.

481
00:32:24,820 --> 00:32:27,490
What's going on?
Why are you sending people away?

482
00:32:27,990 --> 00:32:30,580
Well, ma'am, Ru-ri will be here soon.

483
00:32:30,660 --> 00:32:32,290
Ru-ri, really?

484
00:32:32,370 --> 00:32:35,120
Yes.
We need you to cooperate with us.

485
00:32:35,920 --> 00:32:37,670
Why do you have your gun?

486
00:32:39,050 --> 00:32:41,380
Don't worry about it,
It's in case of an emergency.

487
00:32:41,460 --> 00:32:44,130
Hang on. Why are you all
wearing your guns?

488
00:32:44,220 --> 00:32:46,300
I said, we need you to cooperate with us.

489
00:32:46,390 --> 00:32:47,890
-This way, ma'am.
-Let go.

490
00:32:47,970 --> 00:32:49,850
-Come on.
-What are you planning to do to my son?

491
00:32:49,930 --> 00:32:51,850
-Ma'am, you're coming with us.
-I'm not going.

492
00:32:51,930 --> 00:32:53,060
-Let get her outside.
-Let go!

493
00:32:53,140 --> 00:32:55,190
-Easy, ma'am, okay? Come on.
-Let me go now!

494
00:32:55,270 --> 00:32:57,270
Stop it, you sons of bitches!

495
00:33:08,570 --> 00:33:09,700
Ru-ri!

496
00:33:12,910 --> 00:33:14,500
Get out of my house now.

497
00:33:15,290 --> 00:33:16,210
Kim Ru-ri.

498
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:17,750
Surrender and--

499
00:33:17,830 --> 00:33:19,250
I said get out!

500
00:33:21,300 --> 00:33:23,260
Everyone better get the fuck out.

501
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:25,800
Get out! Right now!

502
00:33:27,680 --> 00:33:28,850
Sure, yeah.

503
00:33:31,640 --> 00:33:34,520
Ru-ri! Ru-ri!

504
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:39,610
Clear out, ma'am!

505
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:44,440
Come on!

506
00:33:45,450 --> 00:33:47,490
It's him! He's got a grenade!

507
00:33:48,110 --> 00:33:49,200
Fall back!

508
00:33:55,580 --> 00:33:57,330
I have eyes on the target!

509
00:33:57,420 --> 00:33:58,460
It's him!

510
00:33:59,420 --> 00:34:01,750
Everyone back! Back!

511
00:34:02,670 --> 00:34:03,920
Get back, everyone!

512
00:34:07,930 --> 00:34:09,510
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

513
00:34:10,010 --> 00:34:13,220
-Stop! Stop!
-Hey! Whoa! Whoa!

514
00:34:13,810 --> 00:34:14,720
Easy…

515
00:34:18,850 --> 00:34:20,350
All right! Don't back down!

516
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:22,020
Everyone, raise your guns!

517
00:34:23,570 --> 00:34:24,570
Form a line!

518
00:34:25,610 --> 00:34:26,610
Don't move!

519
00:34:29,530 --> 00:34:31,780
Why?

520
00:34:34,870 --> 00:34:35,950
Why?

521
